{"tid":1630332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人反抗唔係淨係一句口號","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:48:34.000Z","uid":40443,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"276c973f47a2b781b735b5adf9bb3b8fe56c14c1","tid":1630332,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"發夢今日5點左右係狗總橋下面<br />\n舉左黑旗射左十幾粒之後<br />\n我地拎轉頭一望<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/06/200539_8a4f0f1fe76a6b4e764995d5c96c9989.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2F200539_8a4f0f1fe76a6b4e764995d5c96c9989.jpeg&h=1a40c7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解人都唔多個嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話反抗 點解走哂嘅<br />\n其實我地幾個女仔都好驚架 但我地都肯企前<br />\n唔好再退啦好嗎香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f559e78de87f64eaf0d7afa1b5829785da039398","tid":1630332,"uid":30616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"絲打 香港人愛你<br />\n我都愛你"},{"pid":"5ca3e9383bdca4190c0c97d75a8a257d7e1070f6","tid":1630332,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bc36b270590b628d341b7390004396c8dcd361b7","tid":1630332,"uid":40443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f559e78de87f64eaf0d7afa1b5829785da039398","tid":1630332,"uid":30616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"絲打 香港人愛你<br />\n我都愛你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558e3ad8bac25db2040821d0c4692722c1bfc457