c9989.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2F200539_8a4f0f1fe76a6b4e764995d5c96c9989.jpeg&h=1a40c7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點解人都唔多個嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又話反抗 點解走哂嘅<br />\n其實我地幾個女仔都好驚架 但我地都肯企前<br />\n唔好再退啦好嗎香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人 反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f77921c420af11b10350ebe01fb49fc757ede25","tid":1630332,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5399caefd7bb7f244ab71e9da6f4438dad90d5","tid":1630332,"uid":213656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"15b08870117bb37db1459c9e0a739ceb37cfe1b2","tid":1630332,"uid":40443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bce7a04620fe30f50027b003ebe408efdea08ce","tid":1630332,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"遊行換打陣地次次都輸到仆晒街<br />\n希望你明白 打狗一定係打落單狗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"唔係話要打狗 <br />\n但都唔係前面滅緊火 後面得返幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"唔好見有彈就滅，要走就果斷走"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"根本就唔應該戀戰滅火<br />\n射入人群就話要滅，冇人又滅乜尻<br />\n反抗唔係叫你去同狗渣打陣地，同狗渣多對多，因為你嘅武裝等級根本傷唔到狗，除非你有炸彈<br />\n<br />\n反抗係東有狗你去西破壞，西有狗你去北破壞，北有狗你去南破壞<br />\n有狗走散落單就圍佢打爛佢手腳<br />\n冇狗落單就伏埋等放工，麻包袋，暗殺<br />\n<br />\n樓主仲on99咁話唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔當前線係condom就拉埋未走嘅人走，阿富汗遊擊隊都唔同美國打會戰啦，遊擊啊<br />\n住市區緊係返屋企，有狗經過就投擲通渠水啦"},{"pid":"e0a20d84fbc149268766e9f3f982d2fabfae07